# CI/CD and Automation Patterns

## Continuous Integration Setup

### Maven Build Pipeline
```bash
# Clean build
mvn clean compile test-compile

# Run tests with specific tags
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@Sanity"

# Generate reports
mvn verify

# Package application
mvn package
```

### Test Execution Strategies

#### Suite-Based Execution
```bash
# BizomWebAPI suite
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@BizomWebAPI"

# IntegrationAPI suite
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@Execution"

# Specific module within IntegrationAPI
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@Execution and @Orders"

# Development environment - Quick feedback
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@Sanity"

# Staging environment - Full regression
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@All"

# Production validation - Critical paths only
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@Critical"
```

#### Environment-Specific Execution
```bash
# Set environment properties for different suites
# BizomWebAPI suite
mvn test -Dtest.environment=dev -DbizomWebApiBaseUri=https://devuitest.bizomdev.in/

# IntegrationAPI suite
mvn test -Dtest.environment=dev -DintegrationApiBaseUri=https://devapi.bizomdev.in/

# RetailerAPI suite
mvn test -Dtest.environment=dev -DretailerApiBaseUri=https://retailerapi.bizomdev.in/

# Legacy environment setup
mvn test -Dtest.environment=dev -DbaseURI=https://devapi.bizomdev.in/
mvn test -Dtest.environment=staging -DbaseURI=https://stagingapi.bizomdev.in/
mvn test -Dtest.environment=prod -DbaseURI=https://api.bizomdev.in/
```

## Docker Integration

### Test Container Setup
```dockerfile
FROM openjdk:21-jdk-slim

# Install Maven
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y maven

# Set working directory
WORKDIR /app

# Copy project files
COPY . .

# Install dependencies
RUN mvn dependency:resolve

# Default command
CMD ["mvn", "test"]
```

### Docker Compose for Test Environment
```yaml
version: '3.8'
services:
  api-tests:
    build: .
    environment:
      - TEST_ENVIRONMENT=integration
      - BASE_URI=http://api-service:8080
    volumes:
      - ./reports:/app/target/reports
    depends_on:
      - api-service
      - database

  api-service:
    image: bizom/api-service:latest
    ports:
      - "8080:8080"

  database:
    image: mysql:8.0
    environment:
      - MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=password
      - MYSQL_DATABASE=testdb
```

## GitHub Actions Workflow

### API Test Pipeline
```yaml
name: API Automation Tests

on:
  push:
    branches: [ main, develop ]
  pull_request:
    branches: [ main ]

jobs:
  api-tests:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    
    strategy:
      matrix:
        environment: [dev, staging]
        
    steps:
    - uses: actions/checkout@v3
    
    - name: Set up JDK 21
      uses: actions/setup-java@v3
      with:
        java-version: '21'
        distribution: 'temurin'
        
    - name: Cache Maven dependencies
      uses: actions/cache@v3
      with:
        path: ~/.m2
        key: ${{ runner.os }}-m2-${{ hashFiles('**/pom.xml') }}
        
    - name: Run API tests
      run: mvn test -Dtest.environment=${{ matrix.environment }}
      env:
        BASE_URI: ${{ matrix.environment == 'dev' && 'https://devapi.bizomdev.in/' || 'https://stagingapi.bizomdev.in/' }}
        
    - name: Generate reports
      run: mvn verify
      
    - name: Upload test reports
      uses: actions/upload-artifact@v3
      with:
        name: test-reports-${{ matrix.environment }}
        path: target/
```

## Jenkins Pipeline

### Declarative Pipeline
```groovy
pipeline {
    agent any
    
    parameters {
        choice(
            name: 'ENVIRONMENT',
            choices: ['dev', 'staging', 'prod'],
            description: 'Target environment'
        )
        string(
            name: 'TAGS',
            defaultValue: '@Sanity',
            description: 'Cucumber tags to run'
        )
    }
    
    stages {
        stage('Checkout') {
            steps {
                checkout scm
            }
        }
        
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn clean compile test-compile'
            }
        }
        
        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                sh "mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags='${params.TAGS}' -Dtest.environment=${params.ENVIRONMENT}"
            }
            post {
                always {
                    publishTestResults testResultsPattern: 'target/surefire-reports/*.xml'
                    publishHTML([
                        allowMissing: false,
                        alwaysLinkToLastBuild: true,
                        keepAll: true,
                        reportDir: 'target/cucumber-report-html',
                        reportFiles: 'cucumber-html-reports.html',
                        reportName: 'Cucumber Report'
                    ])
                }
            }
        }
        
        stage('Generate Reports') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn verify'
            }
        }
    }
    
    post {
        always {
            archiveArtifacts artifacts: 'target/**/*', fingerprint: true
        }
        failure {
            emailext (
                subject: "API Tests Failed - ${env.JOB_NAME} - ${env.BUILD_NUMBER}",
                body: "API tests failed for environment: ${params.ENVIRONMENT}",
                to: "team@bizom.com"
            )
        }
    }
}
```

