## Security Testing Integration

### OWASP ZAP Integration
```bash
# Start ZAP daemon
zap.sh -daemon -port 8080

# Run security scan
zap-cli --zap-url http://localhost:8080 spider https://api.bizomdev.in/
zap-cli --zap-url http://localhost:8080 active-scan https://api.bizomdev.in/
zap-cli --zap-url http://localhost:8080 report -o security-report.html
```

### Security Test Tags
```gherkin
@Security
Scenario: Test API security headers
  Given I set up base URI for transactions
  When I send the GET request to "endpoint" endpoint
  Then I should see the response code as "200"
  And verify response headers
    | HeaderName        | HeaderValue |
    | X-Content-Type-Options | nosniff |
    | X-Frame-Options   | DENY |
    | X-XSS-Protection  | 1; mode=block |
```

## Notification and Alerting

### Slack Integration
```java
// Slack notification on test failures
public void sendSlackNotification(String message, String channel) {
    Slack slack = Slack.getInstance();
    SlackMessage slackMessage = SlackMessage.builder()
        .channel(channel)
        .text(message)
        .build();
    slack.send(slackMessage);
}
```

